// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P3492142952" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Backdoor Entry</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Browsing around the internet, you visit less-than-savory blogs such as 'Villains and Molls', 'Evil or Good', and 'Minion of the Day'.  When you're about to visit the last one you see an error message from the server: <br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Serveradmin --- securetoken failure<br><br>Default backdoor access granted<br><br>ComputerName DuskyStar<br><br>FileDirectory -- Secret Paragon Warehouse Stash<br><br>..Files<br><br>....Reminder - Safe Combination!!!.txt</scale></font></color><br><br>There's no way you can't open that file.  Sure it could have a virus, but when has something like that stopped you?"
// Answer Text :
"P2453022051" "HERO: Open the file"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
"P1342464925" "Now is not a good time to investigate this tip.  Wait until you are within the streets of Paragon City before you attempt any investigation."
// Answer Text :
"P385518726" "Investigate this tip later"
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


