// Name :
"P438420260" "A Compromising Photograph"
// LocationString :
// ProfessionString :
// AskAboutTextOverride :
// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1512701915" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Compromising Photograph</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>As you traverse the endless streets and alleyways that make up Paragon City, you find a picture of sorts taped up to an alleyway's wall.  Taking a second look, you find that it's a picture of you holding what seems to be bags of money.  While you're running away from a bank.  And  with a wicked smile on you face.  Turning the picture over, you find a message... to you:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>If you don't want Longbow seeing more of these photos, you'll help them on an upcoming raid.</scale></font></color><br><br>Skipping to the bottom, you see the 'M' you were sure would be there - Manticore's signature."
// Answer Text :
"P743820189" "HERO: Read the rest of the 'suggestion'."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


