// Contact Name : Nocturnal Oneiromancies 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Name :
"P1214026509" "Nocturnal Oneiromancies"
// LocationString :
// ProfessionString :
// AskAboutTextOverride :
// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1198086456" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Nocturnal Oneiromancies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>All of a sudden, you just remembered a dream you had last night.  You were in a cavernous system, deep below the ground and there were people chanting.  One looked up at you, but his face changed to one giant eyeball.  The eyeball said but one thing:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>The treasure has chosen you.  We watch over it, waiting for you.  Claim your destiny.</scale></font></color><br><br>Come to think of it, you've been having that dream for a number of nights now.  Maybe... maybe there really is some treasure out there waiting for you?"
// Answer Text :
"P3530834609" "HERO: Take a chance..."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
