// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1069306048" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Under-the-Table Job</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You get a rather intruiguing email from an old... associate... in the Rogue Isles - Miss Thystle:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>So look, {HeroName}, I know your schtick lately.  Schmooze with all the capes so they get to like you, then when it comes time for them to swing their hammer, you don't get hit so much.  Nice gig.  You always were a wuss, you know that?<br><br>I got a good gig, too.  One that pays a lot.  You remember what that was like?  Gettin' paid in cold, hard cash rather than warm fuzzies and unicorns or whatever crap those heroes are handing out these days.<br><br>Let me get to the point.  I need your skills.  You do this job with me, I give you half, and I don't say a word to your hero friends, okay?<br><br>Freak. </scale></font></color><br><br>The letter then goes on to describe the details of the plan.  It involves that Ice Queen, Polar Shift.  Maybe you can not only teach her to quit acting so high-and-mighty, but also make some secret cash under the table."
// Answer Text :
"P2510533760" "HERO: Go over the plan and what your role in it is."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


