// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1931329116" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Private Punishment</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>On a leisurely stroll throughout the city, you're suprised to see all the TVs in store windows immediately change to a broadcast of a young kid addressing the viewers.  Dressed like a cross between a soldier and an emo kid, the guy specifically calls you by name:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>...{HeroName}!  So this is why I am calling for you to come out of hiding and face me like someone who has a spine!  We will meet on the field of battle and engage in mortal combat!  If you finish me then I, Private Punishment, will forever put away my Wings of War and even - uh, even my Skullface shirt, too!  Just know, that I will always have the higher ground! </scale></font></color><br><br>Were you just called out by some whiney little brat?  No... you HAD to have just imagined that."
// Answer Text :
"P2631242651" "HERO: Find out who 'Private Punishment' is."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


