// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P74556492" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Brutal Discovery</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You come across the Blue Brute, a hero known around Paragon City for not being very bright, but very well-meaning.  He studies you up and down, nods his head, then shoves a letter written with a crayon into your hands:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>PoLees stayshins are not polees they are arrraknose in secret. arrraknose have secret ideyntiteesteesits of gud giys have paswurt but kannt yooz comp yoo tur. passwurt is arraknose123</scale></font></color><br><br>Taking multiple passes at translating it, you realize he's trying to tell you the cops are actually arrrakno -- err, Arachnos agents.  If this is true, that can have some serious implications."
// Answer Text :
"P3032973927" "HERO: Consider what Blue Brute told you."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


