// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1088803272" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Long Protected Armor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>While at the library, you come across an ancient book that details the hidden location of a suit of long forgotten armor.  It also tells of the guardians that need to be commanded in order to open the sarcophagus that contains the armor:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>And knowe thee wordes off ancient byndings.  Upon tablets three shall ye find what ye seek.</scale></font></color><br><br> The book also shows the location of where the armor may have been lost centuries ago."
// Answer Text :
"P1874948243" "HERO: Seek out the ancient armor."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
